name: Hamilton-WenhamElementaryLunchMenu
0:
”Alexa, ask hamilton elementary what's for lunch.”
”Alexa, ask hamilton elementary what's for lunch tomorrow.”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: hamilton elementary
des: If you are like me, every day you are checking your lunch print-out on the family bulletin board so you can make the 'buy or bring' decision for your children. This Alexa skill will tell you what's for lunch today or tomorrow, so you no longer need to print out and squint at the lunch calendar.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
